title: Here is your Week 6 HS football rundown
text:
Here is your Week 6 HS football rundown Game of the Week: Shadow Hills @ Twentynine Palms Patrick Edgell , Digital Content Director, patrick.edgell@kesq.com POSTED: 12:59 PM PDT Oct 09, 2015 UPDATED: 01:00 PM PDT Oct 09, 2015 KESQ THOUSAND PALMS, Calif. - 
Week 6 of the high school football season in the Coachella Valley is upon us. Check out the rundown and come back Friday night to see the full scoreboard. Related Content Suspected DUI driver causes wrong-way crash on Hwy 86 
Blake Arthur and Angelo Caruso will have all of the highlights on the Best Local Sports Show (#BLSS) Friday night at 11 p.m. on KESQ News Channel 3. And be sure to vote for the Play of the Week, which will be posted here around 11 p.m.
